Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard I was chosen by Shinjyu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was something remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't realize\Nwhat the significance of it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But hearing that this enemy\Nwould destroy the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I had to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning,\NI was just fighting feverishly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So little did I know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would end up fighting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter made the miso soup today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,GRADE 6\NCLASS 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,PEACEFUL MORNING,\NRICH COUNTRY, STRONG ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good morning.\N-Good morning, Washio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the classroom,\Nand it's before the morning homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Washio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gin Minowa, you're late.\N-Ouch, miss, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, late as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gin-chan, why were you late today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot that goes on\Nwhen you're in 6th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Class helper of the day, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We are here today because of Shinjyu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us bow to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to fulfill our roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like this before.\NIs this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjyu-sama's sacred boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 1\NSUMI WASHIO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of sacred boundary\Nthat Shinjyu-sama created?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A world of trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like they taught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. It's all trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wonder if that's the Long-Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridge that connects this side\Nto beyond the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the enemy comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we're the heroes\Nmakes me so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san, this isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the enemy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When it crosses the bridge\Nand finds its way to Shinjyu-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's fulfill our roles.\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that come from heaven and earth shall not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As a god, declare your arrival and presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Souls rise up\Nto call down the power of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods called down by the souls\Nare summoned now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, our first actual fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done a joint training yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy appeared earlier than predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's deal with this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm gonna knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is huge.\NIt's so different from our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it so strange that this place\Nwas originally a city, Washio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-This must be...\N-The thing that came from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Vertex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, look.\N-A corrosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer it takes to beat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll have a more harmful effect\Non the original city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait.\N-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A swift attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nogi-san.\N-Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot this turns into a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a huge typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Washio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,YUKI YUNA IS A HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My arrows can't damage it enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san is strong, but she can't get near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to manage Nogi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's dangerous. You have to keep moving.\N-Minowa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She drank the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For a hero with the power of God,\Nit's easy to drink up all the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Mino-san.\NWhat did it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It tasted like cider at the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then it changed into oolong tea midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, the Vertex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It has so many wakemitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry,\Nit'll leave the Long-Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to fight it off if it leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go again with sheer determination.\N-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This spear can turn into a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's handy, Sonoko.\N-Keep on marching forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heroes should have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Push it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you too, Washio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave. Heave. Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now!\N-Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Washio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, I'm going to swing you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony of chinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mino-san, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I weakened it with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, it has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did we...?\N-Beat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-We did it!\N-We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yay, yay, yay!\N-Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, we're not back to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap, I'm in my indoor shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a photo of the world of trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the world of trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Washio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a narrow victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have won against it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW TO MAKE FRIENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As I told you all yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,these three have important roles\Nto fulfill for Shinjyu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So there will be times when they will\Nsuddenly disappear from the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't panic or make a fuss about it,\Nand calmly support the three of them in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have the duty to study hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,GRADE 6\NCLASS 2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is your role hard to do? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not supposed to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? You're such a meanie.\N-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on, tell us.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nogi-san, Minowa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're available,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how about a triumphal celebration after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very pleased that we were able\Nto welcome today without any accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Era of the Gods, year 298.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is the triumphal celebration\Nfor the heroes' first battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish for all your continued prosperity,\Nhealth, and bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too formal. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sumisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about asking you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had trouble bringing it up,\Nso I'm really happy you asked us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't this the first time\Nthat you asked us out, Washio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we haven't had\Nany joint training,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did pretty well in our first battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I got so excited,\NI've been wanting to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I also wanted to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you two out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,don't think I really trusted you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because I hated you guys or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at relying on other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were on my own,\NI probably couldn't have done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you guys were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be friends with me from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become good friends\Nwith you too, Sumisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm not good at making friends either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumisuke, you were feeling the same way too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm glad, Sumisuke.\N-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nogi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that name "Sumisuke"?\NYou started calling me that out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was calling you\Nby a nickname without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about Wasshina?\NDoesn't it sound like an idol's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to be called\NSonokorin either, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about Wasshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stay good friends, Wasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Then call me Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minowa-san is too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate today by eating\Nthe amazing gelato from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These roasted green tea and Calpis flavors\Nare spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How about yours, Mino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Shoyu-Mame gelato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? It looks good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The balance of this bittersweet green tea flavor\Nis perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a bite of it, if it's that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never done anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our first collaborative work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the right way to use that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do something like this\Nwith a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Wasshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Me too. Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm glad.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,YUKI YUNA IS A HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A bud of happiness in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a silver glow\NI'll show it to you when it blossoms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the album that I looked back on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like that back then, and it still is now\NWe're laughing together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The season which gets colored from the south
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say "I'm back."\NI'll definitely come to welcome you straight away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you and start running\NTo a place where no one can catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to fulfill it\NThe promise from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you patiently for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back\NPlease don't ever leave me again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Era of the Gods, year 298.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story of three heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A fairy tale of three girls\Nwho were chosen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always an innocent girl who gets chosen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And in many cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the end result is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ON NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's kind of like Battleship Nagato...\N-What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is weird...!\N-Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's share who we have a crush on!\N-I can help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Training doesn't end until we are home!\N-Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE\NFRIENDS
